sound gravitational wave detectors to optical\nclocks, the dramatic improvement in coherence, bandwidth and precision now\nwithin reach will be decisive in the creation of a new class of quantum\nsensors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 14:55:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Sep 2021 16:01:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-28"}
