 better scalability with respect to mesh refinement than\nthe system AMG, but is relatively less robust with respect to Lundquist number\nscaling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Dec 2020 15:39:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-15"}
